[[File:ChadHilse-ANH.png|250px|thumb|A marine aboard the [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']].]]
'''Rebel marines''', also known as '''Alliance Fleet troopers''' were a class of [[Soldier/Legends|soldiers]] in the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. They were stationed aboard [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Alliance Fleet]] [[Starship/Legends|starships]] for ship board defense and boarding. They were divided into [[Alliance Fleet Regiment]]s in the [[Alliance Military/Legends|Alliance Military]]. [[Ensign/Legends|Ensign]] [[Cariso Smadis/Legends|Cariso Smadis]] was a Rebel marine stationed on the [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]]. The [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends#1st Regiment SpecForce SpaceOps Regiment|1st Regiment]] of the [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Alliance Special Forces]] were a special class of Rebel marines. They later were reformed into the [[New Republic Marine]]s.

==Weapons==
Marines were armed with a variety of weapons, including [[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifles]], [[Missile launcher/Legends|rocket launchers]], and [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonators]]. However, those who were on board the [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']] had only [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistols]].

